### GET Request with parameters
GET http://localhost:8000/api/configuration/social-media-manager
Accept: application/json

### Basic PUT Request
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/configuration
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": ""
}

### PUT Request with additional headers
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/items/2
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer your-auth-token

